content.rendered:
Directed by A.R. Murugadoss

Written by Ranjeet Bahadur. John Mahendran. A.R. Murugadoss

Cast Rajinikanth (Aadithya Arunachalam). Nayanthara (Lilly). Nivetha Thomas (Valli). Suniel Shetty (Hari Chopra (as Sunil Shetty)). Yogi Babu (Kaushik (Adithya’s Assistant)). Gautam Singh Rajput (Goon). Prateik Babbar (Ajay Malhotra (as Prateik)). Nawab Shah (Vinod Malhotra). Dalip Tahil (Chief Secretary). Jatin Sarna (Police Inspector). Sriman (Lilly’s Cousin). Guru Bhullar (Police Man). Shamata Anchan (Lady Cop). Mirabel Stuart (Policewoman). David P Perlmutter (Policeman). Tanmay Nagar (Rahul – adidas showroom). Yograj Singh (Gangster Head). Jeeva Subramanian (‘Kannula Thimuru’ dancer). Surender Thakur (Gangster). Adithya Shivpink (Impersonator). Mithun Purandare (Gangster). Wong Charlie (Triad boss). Nii Ashiboye (Bodyguard). David Gris (Bodyguard). Emerson Kandu (Bodyguard). Ohu Leramoh (Bodyguard). Emanuel Offu (Bodyguard). Kingsley Onyia (Bodyguard). Robin Sutherland (Bodyguard). Aasif Khan. Ravi Kishan. Vikrant Koul (Human Rights Officer). Abhinav. Ajay. Nazar Ali. Deepak Anand. Pankaj Anand (Businessman). Ankit. Anmol. Tamanna Arora. Kartik Baba (Goon). Pradeep Bajpai (Jagan Muppala). Anil B. Balecha. Ashok Kumar Beniwal (Jailer). Bharat. Asif Bhatt. Narinder Bhutani (Bodyguard). Sandeep Bose. Bunty. Trilok Chandra. Parimal Desai. Dheeraj Dev (Tapori). Kirti Dharma. Dasy Dolly. Anaya Dubey. Saroj Garewal. Sumit Giri. Shreya Gupto (Thejashwini Desai). Himanshu. Yusuf Hussain (Doctor). Anamika Jaiswal. Jasmine. Ariyan Jibon. Rajive Joshi. Maghan Kalbag. Deepak Kalra (Officer)

Languages Hindi. Tamil

Production Lyca Production
